# Product Guardrails

- Prioritize group planning workflows: shared itinerary, voting, expenses, and role-based collaboration.
- Design for conflict resolution: concurrent edits, schedule collisions, and budget disagreements.
- Keep privacy explicit for location and personal travel data.
- Prefer transparent AI assistance: editable suggestions, user override, and clear assumptions.

# UX Expectations

- Mobile-first interactions for on-trip usage.
- Fast perceived performance for list/map transitions.
- Accessible components and keyboard-safe interactions by default.
